('91284','31434','5','Very well maintained detached house in bungalow style in Nova Santa Ponsa'),
('91285','31435','5','Nova Santa Ponsa is one of the most popular residential areas in the southwest of Mallorca. Surrounded by several golf courses and marinas, one also finds in a short connection for, supermarkets, restaurants, medical care and schools.\r\nThis lovely family home in a bungalow style and small sea view, was created in 1994 and renovated in 1999 with quality materials and solid building services. The approximately 2.000m² plot has building capacity for further 340m² of living space. The 280m² existing living space is spread on a residential level with entrance hall, living- dining room, open kitchen, laundry room and 3 bedrooms each with a bathroom en suite.\r\nThere is also a  technology - and storage room located in the basement. For upscale amenities include an oil fired central heating, solar panels, air conditioning cold, fitted kitchen, chimney in the living room and double glazed windows.\r\nIn middle of a beautifull landscaped Mediterranean garden is the approx 4x8m large pool surrounded with sun terraces. A sauna with shower room, a covered hot tub and barbecue, as well as 2 covered carports and a garage round up the interesting offer .\r\n\r\n'),
